Constructor Detail

HoldQ

public HoldQ()
Constructor for objects of class HoldQ. Calls the parent constructor. From the reader object in the parent class, the minimum and maximum value are called and a random number between these values are assigned to the multiplier. The type is set to HoldQ and the Linked List with queue operations are instantiated.
